data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled beneath the mountains on the coveted east bench of North Salt Lake! Boasting great views of the valley below, this single-owner residence is a testament to immaculate care and thoughtful upgrades. Recent enhancements include brand new carpet throughout the whole house complemented by newly installed flooring. The entire home has received a fresh coat of paint and remodeled bathrooms. Stay cozy with fireplaces on both levels, perfectly complementing the brand-new high-efficiency furnace. The tankless water heater and a water-softener system provide the convenience of endless hot water. The home is impeccably clean top to bottom. A fully landscaped backyard features a sprawling grass area beneath the shade of large, mature trees. The balcony and patio are great for lounging and entertaining, while the heated pool is perfectly ready for the summer fun. Parking is a breeze with an extra-large pad capable of accommodating a trailer or RV.
